        public Rod(java.lang.String name,
   int cost,
   int rodID,
   ConfigOptions options,
   long cooldown,
   org.bukkit.plugin.Plugin plugin)
        The default lightning rod
        Parameters:
        name - The name of the rod, shows up in inventorys and on the item
        cost - How many rods get used when you right click
        rodID - The default itemID for the rod
        options - The options that get placed into the config (under: Rods.rodName.options)
        cooldown - The cooldown after using this rod in milliseconds
        plugin - The original plugin, USE OTHER CONSTRUSTOR
